IDOR on Order Access

Summary
User can access orders of other users by changing object identifiers.

Affected Endpoint
GET /api/orders/{orderId}

Vulnerability Type
Broken Access Control (OWASP A01)

Severity
High

Description
The server does not validate ownership of the order before returning details.

Steps to Reproduce
1. Login as normal user.
2. Capture GET /api/orders/5567 in Burp Repeater.
3. Change orderId to another userâ€™s order.
4. Observe order details are returned.

Impact
- Data exposure
- Unauthorized access to sensitive resources

Remediation
- Implement server-side authorization check
-Object Ownership Validation

References
- OWASP Top 10 A01
